If you have never made brisket before-- be careful! This is time consuming and absolutely not worth the effort. I made the sauce and could not bring myself to cook the brisket- it smelled bad and tasted worse- the cloves seemed to overpower everything else and it tasted too sour to pour over my 12 lbs. of meat. I scrapped it all the night before my Seder and made a simpler recipe with wine which was delicious.

